    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, honestly it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still looking and driving like a total dream. No scratches, no weird smells, just pure perfection. I'm really sad to let it go, but I'm excited for it to find a great new home. Come take a look\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love with how it handles!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
