    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly mint condition\u2014it\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's super clean, runs like a dream, and has been garage-kept its whole life. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m sure the next owner will love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
